Human proteins (Vidal) network, part of the Koblenz Network Collection
===========================================================================

This directory contains the TSV and related files of the maayan-vidal network: This network represens an initial version of a proteome-scale map of Human binary protein–protein interactions


More information about the network is provided here: 
http://konect.cc/networks/maayan-vidal

Files: 
    meta.maayan-vidal -- Metadata about the network 
    out.maayan-vidal -- The adjacency matrix of the network in whitespace-separated values format, with one edge per line
      The meaning of the columns in out.maayan-vidal are: 
        First column: ID of from node 
        Second column: ID of to node
        Third column (if present): weight or multiplicity of edge
        Fourth column (if present):  timestamp of edges Unix time
